article_title: Palestinian health ministry says two killed in West Bank.
sentence: Palestinian  health  ministry  says  two  killed  in  West  Bank.

article_title: Palestinian health ministry says two killed in West Bank.
sentence: According  to  the  Palestinian  health  ministry,  two  Palestinian  men  have  been  killed  by  Israeli  gunfire  in  two  separate  incidents  in  the  territory  today.

article_title: Palestinian health ministry says two killed in West Bank.
sentence: A  20-year-old  died  of  his  injuries  after  being  shot  by  Israeli  forces  in  the  town  of  Beit  Ummar,  the  ministry  said,  while  a  25-year-old  man  was  killed  in  the  city  of  Tulkarm.
